com.i2group.apollo.alertfeedservice.transport

Class AlertFeedAndSubscriptionToken

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.alertfeedservice.transport.AlertFeedAndSubscriptionToken

  • public final class AlertFeedAndSubscriptionToken
extends Object
    A container for the ItemIdentifier of an alert feed that adds storage for a subscription token indicating whether a user is subscribed to the feed.
    Since:
    3.0
